data.description: Charming brick ranch centrally located in Virginia Beach and ready for new owners to move right in! Come out and see this open, bright, spacious, and inviting three bedroom home with a nice large family room.  Features include newer double-pane tilt-in windows and a brand new hot water heater. This home has a large privacy fenced backyard, attached garage and plenty of on-street and driveway parking. Close to interstates, shopping, dining, and all the area has to offer!  Seller is offering a $2500 flooring allowance with acceptable offer!
data.whatILove: This low-maintenance brick home is well insulated with newer windows and HVAC.  It has a huge privacy-fenced yard with a paver stone patio that is great for entertaining!  Mature trees also provide shade for indoor and outdoor living.
